Interface IModelElement

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAssembly, IAssemblyDefinition, IAssemblyInstance, IChoiceInstance, IDefinition, IFeatureFlagContainer<F>, IFeatureInlinedDefinition<INSTANCE>, IField, IFieldDefinition, IFieldInstance, IFlag, IFlagContainer, IFlagDefinition, IFlagInstance, IInstance, IModelInstance, INamedInstance, INamedModelElement, INamedModelInstance, IValuedDefinition
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface IModelElement
    A marker interface for Metaschema constructs that can be members of a Metaschema definition's model.
